  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-19-51, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REQUIRE THAT MEMBERS OF THE UNITED STATES ARMED FORCES DISCHARGED FOR A REASON OTHER THAN RETIREMENT SHALL PRESENT A COPY OF THEIR DD FORM 214 WHEN APPLYING FOR THE DISTINCTIVE MOTOR VEHICLE LICENSE TAG AUTHORIZED UNDER THIS SECTION; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
